title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick show, DP talks to ESPN NFL Front Office Insider Mike Tannenbaum about the moves made at the trade deadline. Who was the big winner? Frank Isola shares the latest with the Nets and their potential next Head Coach. Plus, Marcuells Wiley joins us for his weekly appearance to discuss which NFL team surprised him most at the deadline.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
